   const pipe = await pipeline('image-text-to-text', 'onnx-community/Florence-2-base-ft');
   const result = await pipe('https://huggingface.co/datasets/Xenova/transformers.js-docs/resolve/main/cats.jpg', 'Describe this image');
   console.log(result); // [{ generated_text: '...' }]
   ```

2. **Type-checking (if TypeScript/JSDoc tooling is in use):** Confirm `pipeline('image-text-to-text', ...)` resolves to `ImageTextToTextPipelineType` via the `AllTasks` mapped type.

3. **Existing tests:** Run the existing test suite to ensure no regression — the plan adds no changes to any existing class or behavior.

